<P>
 Nation to Buy Equipment From U.S. Firms: The Chinese government has placed a 
$157-million order for power equipment from Westinghouse Electric Corp. of 
Pittsburgh, according to a state-run newspaper.Westinghouse will supply a 
generator to the Yangzhou No. 2 Power Plant in Jiangsu province, the China 
